place.name: CROSBY
place.gazetteerText: CROSBY, a township in Flixborough and Frodingham parishes, Lincoln; 7½ miles E of Crowle. Real property, £3, 359. Pop., 247. Houses, 44. (In 1870-72, John Marius Wilson's Imperial Gazetteer of England and Wales)
